description: This file defines the AgentSession data class used for managing agent session data, including serialization, telemetry, and creation from dictionaries.

classes.name: AgentSession
classes.description: Represents a session for an agent, including session metadata, associated agent info, and methods for serialization and telemetry data.

methods.name: to_dict
methods.description: Serializes the AgentSession instance into a dictionary.

methods.name: telemetry_data
methods.description: Returns a dictionary with telemetry information such as model, creation, and update timestamps.

methods.name: from_dict
methods.description: Creates an AgentSession instance from a dictionary, with validation for session_id.
